","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the edges that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use a polygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"building, a lake, or an area you want to highlight."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolygon","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolygon","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNPolygon"}}}